name: Happy Yak Beef Stew With Vegetables and Potatoes
categories: Beef Stew With Vegetables and Potatoes
description: Hearty beef stew to warm your soul. Loaded with tender chunks of beef, potatoes and vegetables, this stew is satisfying and delicious.Ingredients: dried potatoes (sulphites), freeze-dried beef (beef, onion, spices), sauce [glucose solids, hydrolysed corn protein, whole milk powder, potato starch, corn starch, garlic powder, sugar, caramel (sulphites), yeast extract, onion powder, salt, tomato powder, spices, dried herbs], freeze-dried vegetables (peas, carrots/corn), dried onions.May contain: nut, peanuts, sesame, egg, fish, sea food, soya, wheat and mustard.
